##After a 20% spike in the price of a Redesavir knockoff, real people have spent thirty million on Koi

Wechat, FINANCEAPP

Features, tencent news tencent financial official account, here to read finance!

From the success of the imitations to the ultimate benefits, boreal faces many hurdles. Trading data on Feb. 12 showed the secondary market snapped up chips, while some institutions sold off. And belong to Red West Wei concept shares and Yongtai technology, has been in a number of days after the limit limit, out of the roller coaster market.

Source: Tencent News, author of "periscope, " Zhang Beihai, he xi

Redesivir, the "Miracle Drug" that people hope to defeat the virus, has been successfully copied by 688166.Sh  , which is listed on the Science and Innovation Board, and mass production has started. On February 12, the news directly contributed to the opening of the BORUI medicine sealed trading limit, up 20.01% , the total market value of 21.4 billion yuan.

However, in contrast to the exuberance of the capital markets, an American medical professor told tencent news'prospect that since the US announced the use of the drug to cure a patient, and clinical phase III trials started in China, ridgeway is expected to do well. But until the clinical trial is over, we can't prove that Ridgeville is the cure.

The latest clinical trial registration information shows that Radzivir's phase III trial for patients with severe pneumonia at COVID-19, led by Professor Cao Bin of the China Japan Friendship Hospital, was enrolled on February 10. There were 452 severe cases. According to the design of the clinical trial, the trial was conducted in a randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled manner. The Phase III trial is expected to end on April 27, it has been announced.

After the results of the trial proved that Ridgeville was effective, the company still had to pass the licensing threshold, although the company said in its announcement that it would supply patients mainly through donations and other means during the outbreak. Gilead, the US drug company that patented the drug, needs to license a generic version of the drug before it can be sold.

This also means that from the success of the imitation to the ultimate benefit, boreal medicine is faced with many barriers. Trading data on Feb. 12 showed the secondary market snapped up chips, while some institutions sold off. And belong to Red West Wei concept shares and Yongtai technology, has been in a number of days after the limit limit, out of the roller coaster market.

The Elixir, Ridgeway

Ridgeville, which is used to treat the first US patient with a new coronavirus, was developed a few years ago by Gilead, a US biopharmaceutical company, to target the Ebola virus that is endemic in Africa. But in clinical trials, the treatment of patients with Zaire ebolavirus did not work as well, and when the trial was conducted in conjunction with three other drugs developed for Zaire Ebolavirus, those who were treated with Zaire ebolavirus had the highest mortality rate.

In a paper published in October 2019 by the US National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases, a total of more than 1,400 patients in a clinical trial were randomly assigned to receive treatment with four drugs: ZMAPP, Mab114, REGN-EB3 and Ridgeville, the mortality rate was 49% for patients treated with ZMAPP, 34% for patients treated with mAb114,29% for patients treated with REGN-EB3, and 53% for patients treated with redesavir, the overall mortality rate from Zaire ebolavirus outbreaks was 67% .

Based on the results of such clinical trials, the trial data and safety monitoring committee decided to proceed with the trials of the two drugs with the lowest mortality rates, REGN-EB3 and Mab 114, while discontinuing the trials of the other two drugs, ZMAPP and Ridcevir.

But in the midst of a COVID-19 epidemic, a cure based on a "Compassionate Medicine" formula has turned the silent ridgway into a new hope of choking the disease. Soon after, the China Japan Friendship Hospital announced that it was leading a clinical trial of the drug in the COVID-19.

On February 11, the company announced that it had recently successfully developed the synthetic process and formulation technology of Ridgisivir BPC, and had mass-produced the drug in bulk, mass production of Ridgeville preparations is under way. The company also said that if the product can be approved for sale, during the outbreak will be mainly through donations and other means of supply to relevant patients.

The company also disclosed that so far, it has incurred costs estimated to be about 5 million yuan in the development and production of the raw material medicine and the preparation in Redesavir, and that further scale-up of production is expected to require an additional investment of about 10 million yuan.

Face test results and authorization of two major levels

From the success of the imitations to the ultimate benefits, boreal faces many hurdles.

One of the checkpoints is the ongoing phase III trial of Ridgeville. As for the process of clinical trials, says Wang Liming, a professor at the Zhejiang University, "Radcivir needs to follow the rules of new drug development and not arbitrarily shorten the time and standards of research. Because "no matter how bad the disease is, no matter how badly we want new drugs and vaccines, the laws of new drug and vaccine development can not be broken. "

In its announcement, Burrell also warned investors of the risks involved:

1. Zaire Ebolavirus, developed by Gilead for the prevention and treatment of Zaire ebolavirus infection, has undergone Phase I and Phase II clinical trials abroad, currently, Phase III clinical trials of Redesavir for COVID-19(2019-nCoV) infection are not complete, so there is significant uncertainty about the efficacy of the drug for COVID-19(2019-nCoV) infection. If the results of relevant clinical trials are not satisfactory, the replication technology of Ridgeville has no significant value.

2. If the outbreak caused by the COVID-19 infection (2019-nCoV) is rapidly brought under control and alleviated in the short term, and the number of confirmed patients continues to decrease, even if Redesavir is registered for use in the treatment of the COVID-19 infection (2019-nCoV) , nor is it expected to do much to combat the outbreak.

3. Even if the clinical trial of Radicivir for COVID-19 infection (2019-nCoV) is successful, the company's research and development will eventually be translated into products for the market, still need to obtain the patent holder Gilead Company license, drug clinical, drug approval and other links, this process will be a major uncertainty.

4. The company regards the research and development of Ridgeville's replica as a social responsibility, and if the product is approved for sale, it will mainly be supplied to the patients concerned through donations during the outbreak. Therefore, from the production costs, pricing, sales expectations, etc. , the product is not expected to have a significant impact on the company's operating results in 2020.

The secondary market scramble for chips, institutions to sell

Despite the risk alert, the news of the success of the copycat has sent the secondary market scrambling for chips.

By the close of trading on Feb. 12, the share price of Borui medicine on the Kechuang board had exceeded 50 yuan to 52.12 yuan per share, a more than three-fold increase compared with the offering price of 12.71 yuan.

As the company announced on the 11th to develop a copy of the Red Xiwei raw material medicine synthesis technology and preparation technology, 12, the opening of the stock price was a huge amount of capital on the stock trading board of 20% .

As can be seen from the returns on the trades, the buying funds have taken the lead.

Interestingly, the average money bought in the top five was between 5.1 and 5.22 million.

"This means that no one is eating alone on the chips, buying power is more balanced, " said a hot money trader in Zhejiang Province, which means the future selling will not be too violent.

Among the seats sold, one seat was sold for 4.69 million yuan by the Chengdu East Avenue Business Department of Tibet Oriental Fortune, but the business department did not appear in the bought seats on February 3, this means that the chips it holds are bought gradually over many trading days.

Of the two seats sold, there were agency-specific seats, which sold for 3.2 million yuan. "It's very likely that a product from a public or private offering is starting to break even, " he explains.

Overall, the top five outperformed the top five, selling a total of 10.77 million yuan.

"buying more than selling is not necessarily conducive to the subsequent movement of the share price, " since buying seats is already a potential short position.

Buy More, sell more. "All the funds on the jump charts need to stop winning or losing in the short term. "

An investor is more painstakingly saying, the news that is successful to imitate needs to be treated rationally, read announcement to be excited again. First of all, the results of the Phase III trial of Ridgeville will not be available for another month or so. Moreover, even if a generic drug is made, it will need a license from Gilead before it can be produced and sold. In the end, there will be no effect after the clinical trial is over, there is no specific drug for the treatment of NCP. The best drug is "immunity" , so don't get excited. It just means that the company is capable of producing a generic drug in such a short period of time, and even if clinical trials succeed a month from now, Burrell is donating to patients, and that won't really help the company's bottom line.

Real people once spent thirty million on Koi

On November 8,2019, Borui pharmaceutical landed on the science and Trauma Board. On the eve of the listing, in fact, the controller Yuan Jiandong special interests, has attracted the attention of the Shanghai Stock Exchange.

When the agency checked Yuan Jiandong's bank, the actual controller of borui pharmaceuticals, it found that he was spending heavily on his personal interests.

According to the disclosure, between January 1,2016 and September 24,2019, the actual controller of Borui medicine, Yuan Jiandong, spent a total of 32.285 million yuan on his personal hobby of ornamental fish to pay for the purchase and cultivation of Koi fish.

Sponsor Minsheng Securities on-site inspection of Yuan Jiandong's carp, the purchase and cultivation of carp in the main breeding site located in Suzhou Wangshan.

The announcement also revealed that Yuan Jiandong has won many awards in international and domestic KOI competitions, including the overall champion of the eighteen Chinese Koi competitions, the winner of the all-japan Koi Judging Society, etc. , the awards involved a number of ministerial categories and a variety of, and has been issued by the Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe Awards.
